Iran's drone carrier was struck and sunk by US forces on TP4's first day (Wave 1, Feb 28, 2026). It reportedly carried:
- Ababil-3N carrier drones
- Mohajer-6 armed UCAVs
- JAS-313 stealth drones (Qaher-313 derivative)
- Homa VTOL drones

These were destroyed before deployment, disrupting Iran's planned naval drone component.

